name: MegaWorld
additional_notices: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: Massively multiplayer Web3 city builder strategy game since 2018. Players construct buildings producing resources required by other buildings to operate. Discover vibrant virtual world with real economics - explore, build, craft and trade virtual real estate on Ethereum, BNB Chain and TRON Network. Owned by players, governed by players.
